msgid "Selection criteria"
msgstr ""

#: ./security-guide/section_hypervisor-selection.xml:58(para)
msgid "As part of your hypervisor selection process, you must consider a number of important factors to help increase your security posture. Specifically, you must become familiar with these areas:"
