msgid "Policy changes"
msgstr ""

#: ./security-guide/section_continuous-systems-management.xml:238(para)
msgid "Whenever a policy or configuration management is changed, it is good practice to log the activity, and backup a copy of the new set. Often, such policies and configurations are stored in a version controlled repository such as git."
msgstr ""

#: ./security-guide/section_continuous-systems-management.xml:245(title)
msgid "Secure backup and recovery"
msgstr ""

#: ./security-guide/section_continuous-systems-management.xml:246(para)
msgid "It is important to include Backup procedures and policies in the overall System Security Plan. For a good overview of OpenStack's Backup and Recovery capabilities and procedures, please refer to the OpenStack Operations Guide."
msgstr ""

