#: ./security-guide/section_ssl-proxies-and-http-services.xml:28(para)
msgid "In cases where software termination offers insufficient performance, hardware accelerators may be worth exploring as an alternative option. It is important to be mindful of the size of requests that will be processed by any chosen SSL proxy."
