#: ./security-guide/section_security-services-for-instances.xml:109(para)
msgid "The second option is to use the <link href=\"http://docs.openstack.org/image-guide/content/\"><citetitle>OpenStack Virtual Machine Image Guide</citetitle></link>. In this case, you will want to follow your organizations OS hardening guidelines or those provided by a trusted third-party such as the <link href=\"http://iase.disa.mil/stigs/os/unix/red_hat.html\">RHEL6 STIG</link>."
